[h3 id=AboutTheGame 
	" About the game:
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Difficult? Punch-Out!! is a rom hack of Mike Tyson's Punch-Out!!, which was partially inspired by the Title Defense mode of Punch-Out!! for the Wii. The patch can be found 
	[a href=https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/4476/ rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"here.
	]a
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This hack changes every opponent's patterns and makes it so every punch you take sends you down, with the exception of Super Macho Man and Mike Tyson.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Comments 
	" Comments:
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"It took a few tries to get this TAS to a point where I felt it was submission-worthy, but I finally managed to do it this time. Here are the in-game times for each fight, and the improvements over my last TAS which can be found 
	[a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4W8rHyvUNY rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"here.
	]a
	$LF
]div
