	[li 
		" Glass Joe: 47.61
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"Slightly different order compared to my previous TAS, same time.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		" Von Kaiser: 34.61 (was 35.48)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[div class=p 
	"Kaiser's get-up patern is different than the original MTPO, with one uppercut and then a jab. I originally overlooked this and stuck to a strat that was close to the original game, but I recently found this improvement. This also saves 16 frames of real time.
	$LF
]div
